    "body": "## Steps to reproduce\r\n1. Install the latest Focus Nightly 107.0a1 from 9/21, or Beta 106.0b1.\r\n2. Long-tap on the device's homescreen, to trigger the widgets option.\r\n3. Add the Focus Nightly or the Focus Beta widget.\r\n4. Tap on the microphone icon to trgger a voice message.\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\nThe voice search can be performed without issues.\r\n\r\n### Actual behavior\r\nNothing happens.\r\n\r\n### Device information\r\n* Android device: Samsung Galaxy A6 (Android 5.1.1)\r\n* Focus version: Focus nightly 107.0a1, Beta 106.0b1\r\n* Not reproducible on Oppo Reno 6 (Android 12), Lenovo M10 tablet (Android 10)\r\n* Cannot test on Fenix nightly, because the microphone icon is not displayed at all\r\n* Logcat: [logcat1.txt](https://github.com/mozilla-mobile/focus-android/files/9615233/logcat1.txt)\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/40694158/191469646-0f0e63c8-980d-4768-a8de-bd710d797735.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n",
